{"Name":"Dunearn Road GLS 2","ShortName":"Dunearn Road GLS 2","Description":"Set on a sizeable 205,590 sqft land parcel with an estimated 1,400 sqm of commercial space, Dunearn Road GLS 2 offers up to 335 exclusive residences in one of Singapore\u0027s most exciting upcoming precincts. The site has high value potential, further reinforced by its neighbouring plot attracting 9 competitive bids, signalling strong market confidence.","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/eea96303-d9a9-4bc8-999f-c799a2978e8c","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/eea96303-d9a9-4bc8-999f-c799a2978e8c","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}